The newspaper reported that the secret shots, master-minded by the Chinese government and meant to promote their vaccines, has also been reported in Peru and the Philippines. 

It said in Peru, nearly 500 politically-connected people, including former president Martin Vizcarra were secretly given the vaccine, which was undergoing clinical trial. 

Mr Don Wanyama, the senior press secretary to President Museveni, denied the allegation, saying the country is still waiting for doses of the vaccine and that when it comes, frontline workers will be prioritised. 



